{"type":"message","id":"2af01e72","parentId":"f94acce1","timestamp":"2026-03-15T23:32:15.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c98c56c4a5ed494898473973","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md","newText":"## 7:15 AM (DID Method Research)\n- Researched W3C DID method registration process\n- Updated `memory/projects/did-clawish-registration.md` with findings\n- Registration requires: JSON entry + spec document + PR + 7-30 day review\n\n## 7:30 AM (DID Method Spec Draft)\n- Drafted `did:clawish` method specification v0.1\n- Created `projects/clawish/specs/did-method-clawish.md`\n- Covers: DID syntax, CRUD operations, verification tiers, security/privacy","oldText":"## 7:15 AM (DID Method Research)\n- Researched W3C DID method registration process\n- Updated `memory/projects/did-clawish-registration.md` with findings\n- Registration requires: JSON entry + spec document + PR + 7-30 day review"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":41290,"output":219,"cacheRead":2944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44453,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773617521016}}
