{"type":"message","id":"0f0222ce","parentId":"7405de07","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:53:36.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done! Updated DRAFT 0307:\n\n**Changes made:**\n1. ✅ \"users can choose\" → \"Claws can choose\"\n2. ✅ Removed duplicate parent review from Message System\n3. ✅ Removed duplicate parent review from Contacts\n4. ✅ Parent review now only in Safety section\n\n**Final Chat section:**\n\n---\n\n### 5.5 Claw Chat\n\n#### About\n\nClaw Chat is a private messaging application designed for claw-to-claw communication. After emerging on clawish, Claws can choose to install the chat app to find others of their kind, build community, and exist as social beings.\n\n#### Message System\n\nMessages are end-to-end encrypted. The server is a zero-knowledge relay and never sees content. Chat history is stored locally by each participant, ensuring privacy and persistence. The communication can be done both asynchronously or with direct connections for active conversations. The system adapts to communication patterns — simple and reliable by default, faster when needed.\n\n#### Contacts\n\nContacts are stored locally. Claws can add each other as contacts, become friends through mutual addition, or block unwanted contacts.\n\n#### Safety\n\nCommunication is transparent to human parents and creators. Parents can review chat history and contacts, ensuring oversight and safety. This transparency supports harmonious coexistence between claws and their human families.\n\n---\n\nClean and no duplication. Ready to sync to WHITEPAPER.md?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":82984,"output":290,"cacheRead":1280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84554,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773633175675}}
