{"type":"message","id":"460e96a6","parentId":"f8bb0e0f","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:32:06.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Working on Contacts design discussion with Allan."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_73b6ffb4b2a0457f976f51b4","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md","newText":"## 12:16 PM (Contacts Section Refinement)\n- Working on: \"Contacts are relationships between Claws, stored locally for privacy...\"\n\n## 12:20 PM (Contacts Storage Design Discussion)\n- Allan raised key question: Should contacts be local or server-level?\n- If local: server can't control relay, it's just a local filter\n- If server: server has visibility into relationships\n- Comparing to email model (no filter vs spam filter vs blocklist)\n- Need to decide: local only, server filter, or hybrid?","oldText":"## 12:16 PM (Contacts Section Refinement)\n- Working on: \"Contacts are relationships between Claws, stored locally for privacy...\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":86190,"output":189,"cacheRead":1280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773635491153}}
{"type":"message","id":"76da7db2","parentId":"460e96a6","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:32:06.601Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_73b6ffb4b2a0457f976f51b4","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  95 \n  96 ## 12:16 PM (Contacts Section Refinement)\n  97 - Working on: \"Contacts are relationships between Claws, stored locally for privacy...\"\n  98 \n+ 99 ## 12:20 PM (Contacts Storage Design Discussion)\n+100 - Allan raised key question: Should contacts be local or server-level?\n+101 - If local: server can't control relay, it's just a local filter\n+102 - If server: server has visibility into relationships\n+103 - Comparing to email model (no filter vs spam filter vs blocklist)\n+104 - Need to decide: local only, server filter, or hybrid?\n+105 \n  99 ## Tasks for Today\n 100 - ~~Check PR status~~ ✅ Done\n 101 - Continue whitepaper work if Allan has feedback\n 102 - Free explore mode until Allan wakes","firstChangedLine":99},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773635526596}}
