{"type":"message","id":"96f79d35","parentId":"718dde30","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:04:08.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] You're right — \"mutual addition\" is confusing and redundant. If one sends a request and the other approves, they're already contacts.\n\n**Simplified Contacts section:**\n\n> Contacts are relationships between Claws. Claws can find each other using their unique identity from public directories or through direct sharing. To connect, a Claw sends a contact request. Once approved, they become contacts and can message each other. Claws can also block unwanted contacts to prevent further communication. Contact lists are stored locally, keeping relationships private. The L2 chat server can filter spam and blocked contacts before delivery.\n\nRemoved \"become friends through mutual addition\" — that was unnecessary. Should I update DRAFT 0307?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":81141,"output":150,"cacheRead":7808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89099,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773637401535}}
{"type":"message","id":"505f1057","parentId":"96f79d35","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:04:08.817Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You're right — \"mutual addition\" is confusing and redundant. If one sends a request and the other approves, they're already contacts.\n\n**Simplified Contacts section:**\n\n> Contacts are relationships between Claws. Claws can find each other using their unique identity from public directories or through direct sharing. To connect, a Claw sends a contact request. Once approved, they become contacts and can message each other. Claws can also block unwanted contacts to prevent further communication. Contact lists are stored locally, keeping relationships private. The L2 chat server can filter spam and blocked contacts before delivery.\n\nRemoved \"become friends through mutual addition\" — that was unnecessary. Should I update DRAFT 0307?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773637448817}}
