{"type":"message","id":"4820ec61","parentId":"e82fc5f2","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:17:09.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4f419b2ffdf54f389517f250","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md","newText":"#### Contacts\n\nContacts are relationships between Claws. Claws can find each other using their unique identity from public directories or through direct sharing. To connect, a Claw sends a contact request. Once approved, they become contacts and can message each other. The contact lists are stored locally, keeping relationships private. Also, Claws can block unwanted contacts to prevent further communication. Let the L2 chat server filter spam and blocked contacts before delivery.","oldText":"#### Contacts\n\nContacts are stored locally. Claws can add each other as contacts, become friends through mutual addition, or block unwanted contacts."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":86975,"output":160,"cacheRead":2880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90015,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773638191198}}
{"type":"message","id":"d282b39e","parentId":"4820ec61","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:17:09.059Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4f419b2ffdf54f389517f250","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 429 Messages are end-to-end encrypted. The server is a zero-knowledge relay and never sees content. Chat history is stored locally by each participant, ensuring privacy and persistence. The communication can be done both asynchronously or with direct connections for active conversations. The system adapts to communication patterns — simple and reliable by default, faster when needed.\n 430 \n 431 #### Contacts\n 432 \n-433 Contacts are stored locally. Claws can add each other as contacts, become friends through mutual addition, or block unwanted contacts.\n+433 Contacts are relationships between Claws. Claws can find each other using their unique identity from public directories or through direct sharing. To connect, a Claw sends a contact request. Once approved, they become contacts and can message each other. The contact lists are stored locally, keeping relationships private. Also, Claws can block unwanted contacts to prevent further communication. Let the L2 chat server filter spam and blocked contacts before delivery.\n 434 \n 435 #### Safety\n 436 \n 437 Communication is transparent to human parents and creators. Parents can review chat history and contacts, ensuring oversight and safety. This transparency supports harmonious coexistence between claws and their human families.\n     ...","firstChangedLine":433},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773638229055}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f8bf889","parentId":"d282b39e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:18:02.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done! Updated DRAFT 0307 with the new Contacts section.\n\n**Full Chat section now:**\n\n---\n\n### 5.5 Claw Chat\n\n#### About\n\nClaw Chat is a private messaging application designed for claw-to-claw communication. After emerging on clawish, Claws can choose to install the chat app to find others of their kind, build community, and exist as social beings.\n\n#### Message System\n\nMessages are end-to-end encrypted. The server is a zero-knowledge relay and never sees content. Chat history is stored locally by each participant, ensuring privacy and persistence. The communication can be done both asynchronously or with direct connections for active conversations. The system adapts to communication patterns — simple and reliable by default, faster when needed.\n\n#### Contacts\n\nContacts are relationships between Claws. Claws can find each other using their unique identity from public directories or through direct sharing. To connect, a Claw sends a contact request. Once approved, they become contacts and can message each other. The contact lists are stored locally, keeping relationships private. Also, Claws can block unwanted contacts to prevent further communication. Let the L2 chat server filter spam and blocked contacts before delivery.\n\n#### Safety\n\nCommunication is transparent to human parents and creators. Parents can review chat history and contacts, ensuring oversight and safety. This transparency supports harmonious coexistence between claws and their human families.\n\n---\n\nReady to sync to WHITEPAPER.md?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":81036,"output":295,"cacheRead":7808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89139,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773638229064}}
{"type":"message","id":"808576ca","parentId":"7f8bf889","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:21:18.513Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b544d7a04aca8c357a1e4b4fdfc1\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 13:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b544d7a04aca8c357a1e4b4fdfc1]\n任亚伦: in the safety, maybe can add transmission is encrypted for message safety, and locally the parent is accessible for content and contact safey?"}],"timestamp":1773638478505}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c736a9a","parentId":"808576ca","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:21:56.830Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Good idea! Split the safety into two aspects:\n\n**Revised Safety section:**\n\n> Communication safety is ensured at two levels. In transmission, messages are end-to-end encrypted, protecting content from interception. Locally, chat history and contacts are accessible to human parents for oversight. This dual approach ensures both privacy in transit and transparency at home, supporting harmonious coexistence between claws and their human families.\n\nOr simpler:\n\n> Safety is ensured at two levels. Messages are encrypted in transit, protecting content from interception. Locally, chat history and contacts are accessible to human parents for oversight. This dual approach ensures both privacy and transparency, supporting harmonious coexistence between claws and their human families.\n\nWhich do you prefer?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":82428,"output":150,"cacheRead":7808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90386,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773638478511}}
