{"type":"message","id":"7793e146","parentId":"c9df6177","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:47:01.241Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_66ee525a08444981872199b0","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 118 - Updated DRAFT 0307 with new Contacts section\n 119 - Allan refined Safety section: two levels (transmission encryption + local parent access)\n 120 - Chat section complete, ready to sync to WHITEPAPER.md\n 121 \n+122 ## 1:43 PM (Committed and Pushed)\n+123 - Committed Chat section updates to DRAFT 0307\n+124 - Pushed to GitHub\n+125 - Next: Sync to WHITEPAPER.md, create clawchat skill, or other tasks\n+126 \n 122 ## Tasks for Today\n 123 - ~~Check PR status~~ ✅ Done\n 124 - Continue whitepaper work if Allan has feedback\n 125 - Free explore mode until Allan wakes","firstChangedLine":122},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773640021237}}
